    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies the payload format for packetization of the G.719 full-band codec encoded audio signals into the Real-time Transport Protocol (RTP).  The payload format supports transmission of multiple channels, multiple frames per payload, and interleaving. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
